---
import DesktopLayout from '../layouts/DesktopLayout.astro';
import Window from '../components/Window.astro';
import '../styles/menubar.css';
---
<DesktopLayout title="Privacy Policy — Real Serious Business">
  <Window
    title="Privacy Policy - Notepad"
    icon="/icons/win98/notepad_file.ico"
    path="/privacy"
    backHref="/"
    defaultWidth={580}
    defaultHeight={520}
    defaultX={100}
    defaultY={50}
    noBodyScroll={true}
  >
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%;">
      <div class="win-menubar">
        <button class="win-menubar-btn">File</button>
        <button class="win-menubar-btn">Edit</button>
        <button class="win-menubar-btn">Search</button>
        <button class="win-menubar-btn">Help</button>
      </div>
      <div class="notepad-body">Privacy Policy
Last updated: March 2026
----------------------------------------

OVERVIEW
----------------------------------------

Real Serious Business is a personal blog. This
policy describes what little data is handled
when you visit this site.

DATA COLLECTION
----------------------------------------

This site uses Kit (kit.com) for email
newsletter subscriptions. When you subscribe,
Kit collects your email address and may collect
additional information you voluntarily provide.
Kit processes this data according to their own
privacy policy (https://kit.com/privacy).

You can unsubscribe at any time using the link
included in every email.

Beyond the newsletter, this site does not
collect, store, or process any other personal
data on a server.

  - No cookies from this site

ANALYTICS
----------------------------------------

This site uses PostHog for anonymous usage
analytics (page views, basic interactions).
No personally identifiable information is
collected. See PostHog's privacy policy at
https://posthog.com/privacy for details.

LOCAL STORAGE
----------------------------------------

Your browser's localStorage is used solely to
remember window positions and font preferences
on this site. This data never leaves your
device and is not accessible to anyone else.

THIRD-PARTY LINKS
----------------------------------------

Posts may link to external websites. This site
has no control over and assumes no
responsibility for the content or privacy
practices of any third-party sites.

CLOUDFLARE
----------------------------------------

This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages.
Cloudflare may log basic request metadata
(IP address, user agent) as part of its
infrastructure. See Cloudflare's privacy
policy for details.

CONTACT
----------------------------------------

If you have any questions about this policy,
you can reach out via the contact information
listed on this site.

----------------------------------------
      </div>
    </div>
  </Window>
</DesktopLayout>
